	measure 'TopN Bullet chart' = ```
			
			VAR _Programs =
			    ALLSELECTED ( DimProgramTrack[FamilyAcademicProgramTitle] )
			VAR _Rank =
			    RANKX (
			        _Programs,
			        [Distinct Students DaysBetween],
			        ,
			        DESC,
			        DENSE
			    )
			RETURN
			IF (
			    ISINSCOPE ( DimProgramTrack[FamilyAcademicProgramTitle] ),
			    IF ( _Rank <= 5, [Distinct Students DaysBetween], BLANK () ),
			    [Distinct Students DaysBetween]
			)
			
			```
		formatString: #,0
		displayFolder: Top N Chart
		lineageTag: 3e37a591-a60d-42b2-8796-7eb061032c3b

